  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AuthnStandaloneImpl
    Standalone implementation of Authn, using the HttpSession to store current authentication credentials.
    AuthnTestImpl
    Authn implementation for testing.
    AuthzStandaloneImpl
    A standalone, hibernate-based implementation of the Authz facade.
    ContextStandaloneImpl
    Standalone implementation of Context, using the HttpSession to store current context.

    Testing implementation of Context, which always returns TEST_CONTEXT_ID.
